---
By: Henry T. Hamblin
Locus:
  Page: 427
  Verse: 14
Tags:
  - Service
---
One of the great underlying principles governing our life is service. Most
of us have to work, but do we serve? Do we work in a spirit of service? Do
we work for Life and our fellows? Or do we merely work for self, in order
to make a living?
